The paper also discusses the software architecture and development process, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). The use of model-checking and formal verification techniques suggests the paper may also belong to the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses the step-wise refinement of abstract to concrete concepts, which suggests it may also belong to the category of programming languages (cs.PL).
